<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">⚠️ <strong>Pas</strong> <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">localhost</code> — utilise l'IP <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">127.0.0.1</code></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">5. Installer le certificat Burp (pour HTTPS)</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Si tu veux intercepter du HTTPS :</p>
