65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Problème : Onglet "Proxy settings" ne répond pas</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">C'est probablement un problème d'<strong>interface graphique de Burp</strong>. Essaie ces solutions dans l'ordre :</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Solution 1 — Redémarrer Burp Suite</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ferme complètement Burp et relance-le. Parfois l'UI gèle simplement.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Solution 2 — Vérifier la version Java</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Burp Suite nécessite <strong>Java 17+</strong>. Dans un terminal :</p>
<div role="group" aria-label="Code bash" tabindex="0" class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 group-focus-within/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
