<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Si Java est absent ou trop vieux → télécharge <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://adoptium.net/">Java 21</a></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Solution 3 — Agrandir la fenêtre Burp</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Parfois le contenu de l'onglet est <strong>caché hors écran</strong>. Essaie de :</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Maximiser la fenêtre Burp en plein écran</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Ou redimensionner la fenêtre</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Solution 4 — Contourner le problème via Firefox directement</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Puisque Burp tourne déjà (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Proxy running on 127.0.0.1:8080</code>), tu n'as pas besoin de Proxy settings. Configure directement Firefox :</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Firefox → <strong>Paramètres</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Barre de recherche → tape <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">proxy</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Clique <strong>"Paramètres réseau"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Sélectionne <strong>"Configuration manuelle du proxy"</strong></li>
</ol>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Champ</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Valeur</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Proxy HTTP</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">127.0.0.1</code></td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Port</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">8080</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3" start="5">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Coche <strong>"Utiliser ce proxy pour tous les protocoles"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>OK</strong></li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Teste ensuite</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Avec Firefox maintenant proxifié, visite ton app Django :</p>
