p;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Burp Suite n'est pas sur ton Bureau !</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Je ne vois pas de fichier Burp Suite (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.jar</code> ou <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.exe</code>) sur ton Bureau. Il faut le télécharger.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Télécharger Burp Suite</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Va sur : <strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://portswigger.net/burp/releases">https://portswigger.net/burp/releases</a></strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Clique sur <strong>"Community Edition"</strong> (gratuit) ou <strong>"Professional"</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Choisis <strong>Windows (64-bit)</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Télécharge le fichier <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.exe</code></li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">⚠️ Mais attends !</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Je vois dans ton Bureau que tu as déjà Burp Suite qui <strong>tourne</strong> (ton premier screenshot le montrait). Comment tu l'as lancé au début ?</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Via un raccourci ?</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Via un dossier spécifique ?</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Cherchons aussi dans Downloads :</p>
