iv]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">J'ai trouvé le bug exact ! 🎯</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Le problème est dans <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">modify_and_forward</code> — Django écrit le signal dans <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">forward_signal.txt</code> mais le proxy cherche ce fichier <strong>toutes les 0.5 secondes</strong>. Le timing est souvent raté.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">La vraie cause : <strong>Django et le proxy sont dans des processus séparés</strong>, donc <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">proxy_server.forward_pending(proxy_key)</code> ne fonctionne pas — les <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">pending_requests</code> en mémoire ne sont pas partagés.</p>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">La solution — forcer le signal fichier</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Modifie <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">modify_and_forward</code> dans <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">views.py</code>. Ouvre le fichier :</p>
<div role="group" aria-label="Code" tabindex="0" class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 group-focus-within/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
