[&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Parfait ! Je vois la structure dans VS Code</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Tu as :</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">mon_projet</code> (vide)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tuto</code> avec <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">settings.py</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">urls.py</code> etc.</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">manage.py</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">⚠️ <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">burp_app</code> (dossier inutile)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Je vais générer tous les fichiers nécessaires</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Commençons par les fichiers critiques. Clique sur chaque fichier dans VS Code pour l'ouvrir et colle le contenu.</p>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Fichier 1 — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">mon_projet/__init__.py</code></h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Crée ce fichier vide dans VS Code — clic droit sur <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">mon_projet</code> → <strong>New File</strong> → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">__init__.py</code> → laisse vide.</p>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Fichier 2 — Vérifions <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tuto/settings.py</code></h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ouvre <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tuto/settings.py</code> dans VS Code et dis-moi ce que tu vois — notamment la section <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">INSTALLED_APPS</code> et <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">DATABASES</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Comme ça je saurai si je dois modifier <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">settings.py</code> ou juste recréer les fichiers manquants dans <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">mon_projet</code> ! 🎯</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
